A platform dedicated to creating a vigorous environment for both writers and readers to bring back the joy of reading.
For writers: 
Writers can use markdown editor which supports markdown syntax and html to upload their article, and select pictures from Unsplash(open photo library).
For readers: 
Readers can browse through every article with tags, category, search and can collect, leave a comment and like to certain articles.

